## 5. 검증 (cURL 테스트)

```bash
# 인증 없이 public 엔드포인트 접근 → 200 OK
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/public/health

# ADMIN 권한으로 admin 엔드포인트 접근 → 200 OK
curl -X GET -u admin:admin123 http://localhost:8080/api/admin/dashboard

# USER 권한으로 admin 엔드포인트 접근 → 403 Forbidden
curl -X GET -u user:user123 http://localhost:8080/api/admin/dashboard

# 잘못된 자격 증명 → 401 Unauthorized
curl -X GET -u admin:wrongpass http://localhost:8080/api/admin/dashboard
